data.description: Welcome to a 1900's Italianate style facade with decorative brackets under the eaves. The covered porch adds charm and a welcoming touch while a large private yard provides opportunities for outdoor relaxation and recreation. Large shed with cement flooring for extra storage. The interior boasts high ceilings, large kitchen and XL primary bedroom with walk in closet and ensuite bath. Comfortable living space in the dining room and parlor. Upstairs offers 2 bedrooms and a bonus walk in closet or us it as a nursery or office.
